<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>张天硕 — 华东理工大学</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400;1,700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
:root{
  --ink:#1a1916;--ink2:#4a4845;--ink3:#9a9894;
  --bg:#faf8f3;--bg2:#f0ede4;--bg3:#e8e4d8;
  --line:rgba(26,25,22,0.12);
  --accent:#8b3a2a;--accent2:#b85c38;
  --serif:'Playfair Display','Noto Serif SC',Georgia,serif;
  --mono:'IBM Plex Mono','Courier New',monospace;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{font-family:var(--mono);background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;overflow-x:hidden;}

/* NOISE */
body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:9999;opacity:0.35;
background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.85' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.05'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");}

/* NAV */
nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;background:rgba(250,248,243,0.92);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
  border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--line);padding:0 2.5rem;height:52px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;}
.nav-logo{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:-0.3px;}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:2rem;list-style:none;}
.nav-links a{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink3);text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.2s;}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--accent);}
.nav-badge{font-size:9px;padding:2px 7px;background:var(--accent);color:var(--bg);letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-left:6px;vertical-align:middle;}

/* SCROLL BAR */
.scroll-line{position:fixed;top:52px;left:0;height:2px;background:var(--accent);width:0%;z-index:200;transition:width 0.08s linear;}

/* CONTAINER */
.container{max-width:920px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;}

/* ── HERO ── */
#hero{padding-top:52px;min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--line);}
.hero-inner{padding:4rem 2.5rem;max-width:920px;margin:0 auto;width:100%;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 300px;gap:0;align-items:start;
  animation:fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.05s both;}

@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}

.hero-left{padding-right:3rem;border-right:0.5px solid var(--line);}
.masthead-top{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-bottom:2rem;padding-bottom:1rem;border-bottom:2px solid var(--ink);}
.edition{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink3);}
.mag-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:13px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.05em;color:var(--ink);}
.kicker{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:1rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
.kicker::before{content:'';display:block;width:20px;height:1px;background:var(--accent);}
h1.headline{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(34px,4.5vw,54px);font-weight:900;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-1.5px;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:1.4rem;}
h1.headline em{font-style:italic;color:var(--accent);}
.hero-body{font-size:13px;line-height:2;color:var(--ink2);margin-bottom:1.6rem;}
.hero-cta{display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.btn-primary{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:10px 22px;
  background:var(--ink);color:var(--bg);border:none;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;transition:background 0.2s,transform 0.15s;}
.btn-primary:hover{background:var(--accent);transform:translateY(-1px);}
.btn-ghost{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:10px 22px;
  background:transparent;color:var(--ink);border:0.5px solid var(--ink);text-decoration:none;transition:all 0.2s;}
.btn-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);}

.hero-right{padding-left:3rem;}
.portrait{width:100%;aspect-ratio:3/4;border:0.5px solid var(--line);background:var(--bg2);overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin-bottom:1rem;}
.portrait img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center top;display:block;}
.portrait-label{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;background:var(--ink);color:var(--bg);font-size:9px;
  letter-spacing:0.13em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:7px 12px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;}

.stat-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:0;border:0.5px solid var(--line);}
.stat-item{padding:0.8rem;border-right:0.5px solid var(--line);border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--line);}
.stat-item:nth-child(2n){border-right:none;}
.stat-item:nth-last-child(-n+2){border-bottom:none;}
.stat-num{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);line-height:1;margin-bottom:3px;}
.stat-label{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink3);}

/* SECTIONS */
section{padding:5rem 0;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--line);opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);transition:opacity 0.65s ease,transform 0.65s ease;}
section.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
.section-header{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem;padding-bottom:1rem;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--line);}
.section-num{font-size:10px;color:var(--ink3);letter-spacing:0.1em;}
h2.section-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:26px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.5px;color:var(--ink);}
h2.section-title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--accent);}
.section-rule{flex:1;height:0.5px;background:var(--line);}

/* ABOUT */
.about-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:start;}
.about-text p{font-size:13px;line-height:1.95;color:var(--ink2);margin-bottom:1rem;}
.pull-quote{border-left:3px solid var(--accent);padding:1rem 1.4rem;background:var(--bg2);margin:1.5rem 0;}
.pull-quote p{font-family:var(--serif);font-style:italic;font-size:15px !important;line-height:1.65 !important;color:var(--ink) !important;margin-bottom:5px !important;}
.pull-quote cite{font-size:10px;color:var(--ink3);letter-spacing:0.1em;display:block;}

.timeline{list-style:none;}
.timeline-item{display:grid;grid-template-columns:90px 1fr;gap:0.8rem;padding:1rem 0;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--line);}
.timeline-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.tl-year{font-size:10px;color:var(--accent);font-weight:500;padding-top:3px;letter-spacing:0.05em;}
.tl-org{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:3px;}
.tl-role{font-size:11px;color:var(--ink3);}

/* ACADEMICS */
.academics-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:0;border:0.5px solid var(--line);}
.acad-card{padding:1.3rem;border-right:0.5px solid var(--line);text-align:center;}
.acad-card:last-child{border-right:none;}
.acad-big{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:32px;font-weight:900;color:var(--ink);line-height:1;margin-bottom:5px;}
.acad-big span{font-size:14px;font-weight:400;}
.acad-label{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink3);}
.acad-sub{font-size:10px;color:var(--accent);margin-top:4px;font-weight:500;}

.research-box{border:0.5px solid var(--line);padding:1.5rem;margin-top:1.5rem;background:var(--bg2);}
.research-title{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink3);margin-bottom:1rem;padding-bottom:8px;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--line);}
.research-content{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2rem;}
.research-item-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:6px;}
.research-item-title em{font-style:italic;}
.research-item-desc{font-size:12px;line-height:1.85;color:var(--ink2);}

/* SKILLS */
.skills-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:0;border:0.5px solid var(--line);}
.skill-card{padding:1.4rem;border-right:0.5px solid var(--line);border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--line);transition:background 0.2s;}
.skill-card:hover{background:var(--bg2);}
.skill-card:nth-child(3n){border-right:none;}
.skill-card:nth-last-child(-n+3){border-bottom:none;}
.skill-cat{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:7px;}
.skill-name{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:10px;}
.skill-bar-wrap{margin-bottom:10px;}
.skill-bar-label{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:9px;color:var(--ink3);margin-bottom:4px;}
.skill-bar{height:2px;background:var(--bg3);position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.skill-bar-fill{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;background:var(--ink);width:0;transition:width 1.3s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);}
.skill-bar-fill.red{background:var(--accent);}
.skill-tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;margin-top:8px;}
.tag{font-size:9px;padding:3px 7px;border:0.5px solid var(--line);color:var(--ink3);letter-spacing:0.05em;transition:all 0.2s;}
.tag:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);}

/* ACTIVITIES */
.activities-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1.5rem;}
.activity-card{border:0.5px solid var(--line);padding:1.3rem;}
.ac-icon{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:8px;}
.ac-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:6px;}
.ac-desc{font-size:12px;line-height:1.85;color:var(--ink2);}
.ac-badge{display:inline-block;font-size:9px;padding:2px 8px;background:var(--ink);color:var(--bg);letter-spacing:0.1em;margin-top:8px;}
.ac-badge.green{background:#3a7a5a;}

/* CERTIFICATES */
.certs-intro{font-size:12px;line-height:1.85;color:var(--ink2);margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.certs-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:0;border:0.5px solid var(--line);}
.cert-item{border-right:0.5px solid var(--line);border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--line);overflow:hidden;cursor:pointer;transition:background 0.2s;}
.cert-item:hover{background:var(--bg2);}
.cert-item:nth-child(3n){border-right:none;}
.cert-item:nth-last-child(-n+3){border-bottom:none;}
.cert-img-wrap{width:100%;aspect-ratio:4/3;overflow:hidden;background:var(--bg3);}
.cert-img-wrap img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;transition:transform 0.4s;}
.cert-item:hover .cert-img-wrap img{transform:scale(1.04);}
.cert-caption{padding:0.8rem;border-top:0.5px solid var(--line);}
.cert-name{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:2px;}
.cert-date{font-size:9px;color:var(--ink3);letter-spacing:0.08em;}

/* CONTACT */
.contact-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;}
.contact-intro{font-size:13px;line-height:1.95;color:var(--ink2);margin-bottom:2rem;}
.contact-links{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;}
.contact-link-item{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:1rem 0;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--line);text-decoration:none;color:var(--ink);transition:all 0.2s;}
.contact-link-item:first-child{border-top:0.5px solid var(--line);}
.contact-link-item:hover{padding-left:8px;color:var(--accent);}
.cl-left{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;}
.cl-label{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink3);}
.cl-val{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;}
.cl-arrow{font-size:16px;transition:transform 0.2s;}
.contact-link-item:hover .cl-arrow{transform:translateX(4px);}
.aside-col{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.2rem;}
.aside-box{border:0.5px solid var(--line);padding:1.3rem;background:var(--bg2);}
.aside-title{font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink3);margin-bottom:0.8rem;padding-bottom:7px;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--line);}
.aside-text{font-size:12px;line-height:1.85;color:var(--ink2);}
.status-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#3a7a5a;display:inline-block;margin-right:6px;vertical-align:middle;}

/* FOOTER */
.ornament{text-align:center;color:var(--ink3);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.3em;margin:2rem auto 1rem;max-width:920px;padding:0 2.5rem;}
footer{padding:1.8rem 2.5rem;border-top:2px solid var(--ink);display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;max-width:920px;margin:0 auto;}
.footer-copy{font-size:10px;color:var(--ink3);letter-spacing:0.08em;}
.footer-sig{font-family:var(--serif);font-style:italic;font-size:13px;color:var(--ink2);}

/* LIGHTBOX */
.lightbox{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(26,25,22,0.9);z-index:1000;align-items:center;justify-content:center;cursor:pointer;}
.lightbox.open{display:flex;}
.lightbox img{max-width:90vw;max-height:88vh;object-fit:contain;border:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);}
.lb-close{position:absolute;top:1.5rem;right:2rem;color:rgba(250,248,243,0.6);font-size:24px;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--mono);letter-spacing:0.1em;}

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media(max-width:700px){
  nav{padding:0 1rem;}
  .nav-links{display:none;}
  .hero-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:2rem;padding:2.5rem 1rem;}
  .hero-left{border-right:none;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--line);padding-right:0;padding-bottom:2rem;}
  .hero-right{padding-left:0;}
  .about-grid,.contact-layout,.research-content{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .academics-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;border:none;gap:0;}
  .acad-card{border:0.5px solid var(--line);margin:-0.5px;}
  .skills-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}
  .skill-card:nth-child(3n){border-right:0.5px solid var(--line);}
  .skill-card:nth-child(2n){border-right:none;}
  .skill-card:nth-last-child(-n+3){border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--line);}
  .skill-card:nth-last-child(-n+2){border-bottom:none;}
  .activities-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .certs-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}
  .certs-grid .cert-item:nth-child(2n){border-right:none;}
  .certs-grid .cert-item:nth-child(3n){border-right:0.5px solid var(--line);}
  footer{flex-direction:column;gap:8px;text-align:center;padding:1.5rem 1rem;}
  .container,.hero-inner{padding-left:1rem;padding-right:1rem;}
  section{padding:3rem 0;}
}

.course-block{border:0.5px solid var(--line);padding:1.5rem;margin-top:1.5rem;background:var(--bg2);}
.course-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:0;margin-top:1rem;border:0.5px solid var(--line);}
.course-item{padding:1rem 0.8rem;border-right:0.5px solid var(--line);border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--line);transition:background 0.2s;}
.course-item:hover{background:var(--bg3);}
.course-item:nth-child(4n){border-right:none;}
.course-item:nth-last-child(-n+4){border-bottom:none;}
.course-item.highlight .course-score{color:var(--accent);}
.course-score{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:26px;font-weight:900;line-height:1;margin-bottom:4px;color:var(--ink);}
.course-name{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:var(--ink);margin-bottom:3px;line-height:1.4;}
.course-meta{font-size:9px;color:var(--ink3);letter-spacing:0.06em;margin-bottom:8px;}
.course-bar{height:2px;background:var(--bg3);position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.course-bar-fill{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;bottom:0;background:var(--ink);width:0;transition:width 1.4s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1);}
.course-item.highlight .course-bar-fill{background:var(--accent);}
.course-note{font-size:10px;color:var(--ink3);margin-top:1rem;padding-top:0.8rem;border-top:0.5px solid var(--line);letter-spacing:0.05em;}
@media(max-width:700px){.course-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}.course-item:nth-child(4n){border-right:0.5px solid var(--line);}.course-item:nth-child(2n){border-right:none;}.course-item:nth-last-child(-n+4){border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--line);}.course-item:nth-last-child(-n+2){border-bottom:none;}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="scroll-line" id="scrollLine"></div>
<div class="lightbox" id="lightbox"><span class="lb-close">× close</span><img id="lbImg" src="" alt=""></div>

<nav>
  <a class="nav-logo" href="#hero">张天硕 · 华理<span class="nav-badge">本科生</span></a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">简介</a></li>
    <li><a href="#academics">学术</a></li>
    <li><a href="#skills">技能</a></li>
    <li><a href="#activities">活动</a></li>
    <li><a href="#certs">证书</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">联系</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- ── HERO ── -->
<div id="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-left">
      <div class="masthead-top">
        <span class="mag-title">张天硕 · 个人档案</span>
        <span class="edition" id="today-date"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="kicker">Cover Story</div>
      <h1 class="headline">
        化工学院的<br>
        <em>跨界探索者</em>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-body">
        华东理工大学化工学院油气储运专业本科生，
        专业排名第一（1/91），致力于将扎实的工科底蕴
        与新兴的人工智能技术融合贯通。
        科研路上，我在实验室探索荧光材料的秘密；
        学习之余，我在代码里寻找另一种优雅。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#academics" class="btn-primary">查看学术成果 →</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-ghost">联系我</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-right">
      <div class="portrait">
        <img src="/images/profile-id-photo.png" alt="个人照片">
        <div class="portrait-label">
          <span>华东理工大学</span>
          <span>化工学院</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-row">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-num">1<span>/91</span></div>
          <div class="stat-label">专业排名</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-num">90.4</div>
          <div class="stat-label">综合素质分</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-num">200<span>h+</span></div>
          <div class="stat-label">志愿时长</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-num">583<span>/540</span></div>
          <div class="stat-label">四级/六级</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── ABOUT ── -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-num">01</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">关于 <em>我</em></h2>
      <div class="section-rule"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>
          我就读于华东理工大学化工学院油气储运工程专业，学习成绩优异，品德优良。
          专业综合排名第一（1/91），并获综合素质评价分90.4分。
          学习之余，我通过了班级入党积极分子推优，始终以更高的标准要求自己。
        </p>
        <p>
          在科研方向，我加入了贺晓鹏导师课题组，
          从事 VIE 荧光诱导发光材料的合成与性能改进研究，
          并入选学校创新人才培养计划，开始系统性地参与科研工作。
